about.summary: Python bindings and utilities for GeoJSON

name: geojson
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.3.3" %}


package:
    name: geojson
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: geojson-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/g/geojson/geojson-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: 2da9a02548ff783bb1f4c3624e31cf78

build:
    number: 0
    preserve_egg_dir: True
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - geojson

about:
    home: https://github.com/frewsxcv/python-geojson
    license: BSD 3-Clause
    summary: Python bindings and utilities for GeoJSON

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
